snippet.title: Over Rs 10 crore in Cash Seized in Raids on a Law Firm in Greater Kailash Part 1

localized.description:
Over Rs 10 crore in cash seized in raids on a law firm in Greater Kailash Part 1 in Delhi. Hundreds of crore cash which include old Rs 500 and Rs 1000 notes and new Rs 2000 notes have been seized in the raids by Income tax department across the country while people are standing in queues outside banks and ATMs. Many corrupt bank employees have been suspended and transferred for converting black money into white.
